CT Tenants have the following protections: 
-Landlords must apply for UniteCT rental assistance prior to delivering an eviction notice;
-Landlords are required to give at least 30-days notice;
-A stay in eviction proceedings of up to 30 days if landlord/tenant applies to UniteCT.
